data.text:
The most iconic holiday record in the Verve repertoire, and one of the most successful jazz holiday albums of all time is receiving new life for the 2023 season with a new cover!

New first-ever “Ruby Red” color variant with a new Ella-focused collectable cover. Ranked #10 on Rolling Stone’s 25 Greatest Christmas Albums of All Time and ranked #2 on The Guardian’s 20 Greatest Holiday Albums Ever. “The best holiday album ever” (Salon). Jingle Bells; Sleigh Ride; Winter Wonderland; and more!
